paragraphs.title: Upload Data to Master Cluster
paragraphs.text:
f%sh
if ! hdfs dfs -test -e "/user/zeppelin/Year2010-2011.csv"; then

    wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ekachaiou/KMUTT-PROJ/master/Year2010-2011.zip

    unzip Year2010-2011.zip
    hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /user/zeppelin/kmutt
    hdfs dfs -put Year2010-2011.csv /user/zeppelin/kmutt
fi

%pyspark
# get distinct product id in rules
prodId=associationRules.rdd.flatMap(lambda x:x.antecedent+x.consequent).distinct().collect()
prodId=[[i] for i in prodId]
prodInRules=sc.parallelize(prodId).toDF(['prod_id'])
prodInRules.show()

%pyspark
# get product name
prodInRules.registerTempTable("prodInRules")
freqProduct=spark.sql("SELECT stockcode, description FROM prodInRules JOIN marketbasket.items ON prodInRules.prod_id=items.stockcode");
freqProduct.show(truncate=False)
